org.jdesktop.swingx.table
Interface RowModel<_RowType>

Type Parameters:
_RowType - The type of each row in the JTable
All Known Subinterfaces:
RowModel.Editable<_RowType>, RowModel.Expandable<_RowType>
All Known Implementing Classes:
RowModel.ArrayRowModel, RowModel.ListRowModel
public interface RowModel<_RowType>

Support class for SeparatedTableModel. In most cases you don't use this class directly. Instead, you let the SeparatedTableModel instantiate an inner class of this interface in its constructor.

Author:
Miguel Muñoz
See Also:
SeparatedTableModel
